New York State Senator John Sampson
was charged with embezzlement, obstruction of justice and making
false statements for allegedly using stolen funds for a bid to
become  district attorney  in Brooklyn, New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christie Smythe in Brooklyn at 
 csmythe1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
